Description: GNU Radio pulse detection for SensorGnome
 Python scripts for GNU Radio-based RF acquisition and Motus pulse detection,
 replacing vamp-alsa-host for RTL-SDR, Airspy, Airspy HF+, and FUNcube
 Dongle Pro+ receivers.
